Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.76,0:01:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后一个是浑身脏兮兮的老头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.78,0:01:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直念着他那不知道是弟子还是孙子的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.35,0:01:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在让我厌恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.89,0:01:51.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看照片吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.06,0:01:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是研究后的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.11,0:01:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以已经看不清原形了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.82,0:02:09.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的弟子叫什么来着...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.94,0:02:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起来了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.64,0:02:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对研究过后的东西总是没有丝毫...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.25,0:02:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他弟子的名字...让我来告诉你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.75,0:02:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他弟子的名字是...雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石田雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.76,0:02:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人叫做石田宗弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.19,0:02:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的师父 同时也是我的亲祖父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那又怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.01,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上灭却师的自尊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.23,0:02:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要杀了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.05,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经被疋杀地藏封住手脚了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.78,0:03:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还能站得起来...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.08,0:03:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道这是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是乱装天傀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.45,0:03:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由无数丝状的交错结合而成的灵子束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.13,0:03:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将无法动弹的部位连接起来 像傀儡般地强制其运动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.29,0:03:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本是衰老无法灵活行动的灭却师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.13,0:03:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能继续跟虚战斗所想出的招术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.12,0:03:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是肌腱断裂还是骨头碎裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.62,0:03:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这招面前都变得毫无意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.46,0:03:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是为了战斗到最后一刻而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.48,0:03:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是灭却师最强的战斗灵术...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.55,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为它早就失传了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.60,0:04:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 在我所研究的两千六百六十一人当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.88,0:04:08.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连它的皮毛都没有人会使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你这么年轻就会使用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.92,0:04:16.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的...天才吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天才?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.09,0:04:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想被这么陈腐的字眼来形容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.50,0:04:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的乱装天傀不是单纯的防御型招术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.21,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更不是什么延命的招术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想在消除心头之恨前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.70,0:04:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算成为行尸走肉也要\N不停战斗到最后一刻的意识的表现罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.29,0:04:39.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收回天才的称呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.31,0:04:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过是个乳臭未干的小毛孩罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.72,0:04:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.09,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近似乎又去你爷爷那里了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.09,0:04:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该已经说过好几次了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.91,0:04:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你不要再去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要找借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.97,0:05:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这我也说过很多次了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.07,0:05:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拯救死人是毫无意义的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.50,0:05:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.88,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是死神的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.46,0:05:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要学着如何去拯救活人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.74,0:05:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是没有兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.91,0:05:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你是没有才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭却师就在你爷爷那一代结束吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.92,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.07,0:05:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么讨厌灭却师呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那赚不了钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.56,0:05:49.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了...他说的也不无道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.19,0:05:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光靠当个灭却师是养不活自己的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他这个有家的人来说 这是个很重大的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是那种事...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.26,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说得也没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:05.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看得见啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.01,0:06:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"虚"...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.58,0:06:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些遭到攻击的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.50,0:06:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有光靠死神根本应付不来的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.69,0:06:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都亲眼所见 所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸应该也都看见了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.67,0:06:26.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是为什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么能说出那样的话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.96,0:06:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.41,0:06:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.14,0:06:40.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.76,0:06:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想变成厉害的灭却师 保护大家不被"虚"伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.15,0:06:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 爸爸也一定会认同灭却师的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.05,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.95,0:07:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我对你似乎有点兴趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.19,0:07:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定不杀你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要活捉你回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后成为我的研究体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过雨龙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.72,0:07:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该要理解你爸爸的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.46,0:07:25.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要保护的东西不同的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所认同的正义也会不一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸想要保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.97,0:07:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是钱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.91,0:07:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天你会明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等哪一天你明白了这一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.52,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会明白你真正所想保护的东西是什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那一天的来临 雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.51,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这个托付给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.70,0:07:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个叫散灵手套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具有将灵子高级别扩散的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.58,0:08:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能戴着它制出弓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并能保持七天七夜的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就一定能够接近灭却师的极致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.51,0:09:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果到了那个时候 雨龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.56,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能再把它脱下来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 到了那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.19,0:09:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的灵子收缩力将会超越灭却师的极限
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.81,0:09:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物极必反
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.43,0:09:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脱下的话 你可在瞬间得到极致的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.87,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也将会失去作为灭却师的所有力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.22,0:09:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 跟我一起去研究所吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.89,0:09:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前 我还不打算杀你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.87,0:09:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 你会了解你父亲的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.31,0:09:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并找到自己真正想保护的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.15,0:09:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果到了那个时候 你还想继续灭却师之路的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.17,0:10:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你肯定会遇到无法躲避的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.04,0:10:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会遇到自己能力所不及的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.84,0:10:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候你就用这散灵手套吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我再重申一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦戴上了就绝对不能再取下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.31,0:10:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有的是不杀你 还能把你带回研究所去的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.23,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想尝尝地狱般的痛苦的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.83,0:10:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我现在就试试其中的一种方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱装天傀是有极限的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.54,0:10:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是无法一直坚持下去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.17,0:10:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我依然无法了解爸爸的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.72,0:11:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道自己真正想保护的是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.91,0:11:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我清楚地知道什么事情是无法原谅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.74,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我再一次 违背您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让我再一次 违背您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.65,0:11:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么...怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.98,0:11:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.44,0:12:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么形态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这灵压又是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.95,0:12:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西我根本就不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.03,0:12:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.46,0:12:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然在吸收周围的建筑物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.02,0:12:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸魂界的建筑物全是由灵子组成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.17,0:12:34.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他能破坏\N灵子的组合结构并强制将其吸收吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这该叫做灵子的隶属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.02,0:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经超越了人类所拥有的能力范围了 小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.58,0:12:55.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快 不过这种程度我还能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.44,0:13:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭着向我求饶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.26,0:13:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后不要再次出现在我的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样 我就放你一马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.27,0:13:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你拒绝 我就会用比刚才大三倍的力量攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.09,0:13:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太得意忘形了 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个灭却师竟然如此狂妄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.34,0:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 那我也拿出相等的力量来应战好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.69,0:13:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卍解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 卍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.45,0:14:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金色疋杀地藏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.33,0:14:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.55,0:14:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把斩魄刀应该已经解放过一次了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.95,0:14:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩魄刀的解放是有两个阶段的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.44,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.25,0:14:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疋杀地藏是斩魄刀解放的第一阶段 始解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.14,0:14:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而这金色疋杀地藏就是其第二阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.82,0:14:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即卍解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.16,0:14:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它所释放出的猛毒能将你的全部抹杀殆尽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.74,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法对像你这样的异才进行研究实在是可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茧利...大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这...该死的灭却师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.43,0:16:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将斩到的物体化成液体的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可惜啊 灭却师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.57,0:16:43.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的王牌当然是要在这最紧要关头用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.96,0:16:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能逃跑 竟然还留了这么一手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.97,0:16:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.09,0:16:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的我虽然无法做出任何攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却也无法受到任何伤害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几天内我都无法恢复原样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.13,0:17:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我会回到局里 把伤治好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 灭却师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然事情有些许麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我能活着 而你将死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个结局是不会改变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.08,0:17:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灭却师...先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.46,0:17:47.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的左手臂的副官章里有解毒药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.11,0:17:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺着会不会舒服一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 这样就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就在那里面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.15,0:18:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.22,0:18:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体是用跟茧利大人相同的成分制成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.92,0:18:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会被这毒给毒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是觉得这可能是个圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这样的话 请将它倒进我的嘴里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.75,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我喝给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.04,0:18:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对一个将要被毒死的人下圈套 没有任何意义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.60,0:18:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.93,0:18:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你瞄准的是头部的话 就能杀了茧利大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.41,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你并没有这么做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原来确实是想杀他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.63,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有杀死茧利大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解毒药就当是小小谢礼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.12,0:19:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我实在不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.15,0:19:13.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙 为什么你要这么维护...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.75,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是当我知道他还活着时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.08,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微安心了些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.35,0:19:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你喝了就快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过一会 队员们就会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解药 谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.93,0:20:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛 身体好重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.03,0:20:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.38,0:20:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂也渐渐无法抬起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.75,0:20:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.70,0:20:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我作为灭却师的时间快到头了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.93,0:20:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.73,0:20:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的话一定没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.41,0:20:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让那个十一番队的家伙带到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.56,0:20:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.26,0:20:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岩鹫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.81,0:20:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信大家...一定会到这里来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.29,0:20:56.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我是第一个到达的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我将朽木救出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.20,0:21:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎那家伙一定想亲自救她出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.48,0:21:11.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来 他一定会很不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.39,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你无冤无仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为了和平我必须要除掉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.66,0:21:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣叫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.69,0:21:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,清虫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.08,0:22:42.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦变成这样 就暂时无法恢复原样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.24,0:22:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说吃饭了 就连澡也不能洗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.68,0:22:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能待在适当大小的瓶里...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.84,0:22:52.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别加水啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.99,0:22:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会混在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.43,0:22:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比想象的要不便啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.21,0:23:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七番队队长 狛村左阵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看得到前面吗
